						<div class="postbody">Another way to avoid this problem with DPCM may be to disallow any functions while music is playing except to push the &quot;A&quot; button to stop it, and then you can push the direction buttons and START button to play the next music. (I believe the &quot;A&quot; button can be read without DPCM interference.)</div>

					
